description: This package provides the MSBuild, local run and deploy tools that support the CI/CD of Stream Analytics Visual Studio projects. You can find detailed instructions in readme.txt file
releaseNotes:
Add the support for authenticating Azure Data Lake Storage Gen1 using managed identities.
      Enable live data local run in SA.exe.
      Make CustomTime configurable for 'OutputStartMode' property.
      Expose 'ASAApiVersion' as a parameter in the parameter file. Default version is '2017-04-01-preview'. By changing the value in the parameter file will changed the 'apiversion' been used in ARM.
summary: This package provides the MSBuild, local run and deploy tools that support the CI/CD of Stream Analytics Visual Studio projects.
title: Microsoft Azure Stream Analytics CI/CD
